author: The Associated Press
title: Wisconsin GOP vows Supreme Court appeal on extended voting
description: Wisconsin Republicans say they're asking the U.S. Supreme Court to block extended absentee voting in Tuesday's primary
content:
MADISON, Wis. -- 
Wisconsin Republicans say they will ask the U.S. Supreme Court to block extended absentee voting in Tuesday's primary, despite public health fears about in-person voting amid the coronavirus pandemic.
